::Kluster::

Klsuter frowns as he recieves Phobia's responce.

"I'm afraid that's not within my powers," he says into his comm-link, "We 
could leave your crimes on the planet....unmentioned, and bring you back as a 
Maximal, but whatever crimes you made before coming to this planet are not in 
my power to pardon."
